<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="I-wis" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">I-wis</orth> (most M. Edd. <emph>I wis,</emph> i. e. I know), adv. surely, certainly: <bibl n="shak. mv 2.9.68" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 9, 68</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.1.62" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 1, 62</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.102" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 102</bibl>. Per. <bibl n="shak. r3 2.0." default="NO" valid="yes">II Prol. 2</bibl>. In <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.1.180" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 1, 180</bibl> some M. Edd. <emph>I wist,</emph> O. Edd. <emph>I wish.</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>